mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"你喺鏡頭之後打狗無人會理你，但唔好打到記者同first aider 好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6d889a28198bcd05235758bb872f2dfbd21143","tid":1470560,"uid":300403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n重點係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地敢道歉 警察你敢嗎????</span></span>"},{"pid":"0183289526069c8d1cf3d2623d01777079aac645","tid":1470560,"uid":270768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"道歉=承認責任<br />\n絕不能道歉<br />\n改用文宣煲大公安事件、黑狗濫捕"},{"pid":"f2b0baeaee12cd1a4886d05b1d7e2c3c325b0acb","tid":1470560,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"no harm"},{"pid":"3f309aed22dd347cbaeeaefa382e9bbfc36062e4","tid":1470560,"uid":280582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"道歉係處理關公 唔理人做鬼揞眼做<br />\n道歉係我哋有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋敢道歉 警察敢嗎？<br />\n不完美可接受會改變</span></span> 呢句係popo教我講嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打大佬啦各位 大佬放鬼出關公呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不割但要智取捉鬼打關公<br />\n捉到鬼selfie求放朋友圈 多謝參與</span><br />\n<br />\n我地敢道歉 警察你敢嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470560</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDLEEQu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDLEEQu.jpg&h=57a4d3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZxSZQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZxSZQA.jpg&h=1e282855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1de5ed2c2b0ba2cd4e7acfe3f2895cf92761bd1","tid":14